 or I’m craving a liquor-free nightcap. Its hearty dose of probiotics is also said to improve metabolism, immunity, liver function…the list goes on.<p><br><p>Long story short, there are plenty of good reasons to be kombucha curious. And, luckily enough, there are plenty of Appalachian brewers to guide you on your booch (yes, that’s its affectionate nickname) journey.</div></div></div><div id=znid-205059212558 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=heading data-background-type=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false data-text-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><h3 class=zn-heading><a href=https://blueridgebucha.com target=_blank>Blue Ridge Bucha</a></h3></div></div><div id=znid-743917895309 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=text data-background-type=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false data-text-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-text>1809 East Main Street, Waynesboro, Va.</div></div></div><div id=znid-207395660957 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=row data-layout="6-6 6-6 12-12" data-full-width=false data-vertical-align=top data-background-type=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-row data-reverse-lg=false data-reverse-md=false data-reverse-sm=false><div class="zn-column zn-column-lg-6 zn-column-md-6 zn-column-sm-12"><div class=zn-children><div class=zn-child><div class=zn-template><div id=znid-361901413966 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=image data-filter=none data-background-type=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-image><img class=zn-nodrag src=https://media.zenobuilder.com/upload/sp-9949/76222937.jpg alt="" draggable=false></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zn-column zn-column-lg-6 zn-column-md-6 zn-column-sm-12"><div class=zn-children><div class=zn-child><div class=zn-template><div id=znid-755751012887 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=image 